io.reinert.requestor.core

Enum Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Status>
      • io.reinert.requestor.core.Status
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event, HttpStatus, Serializable, Comparable<Status>

    public enum Status
extends Enum<Status>
implements HttpStatus
    Commonly used status codes defined by HTTP, see HTTP/1.1 documentation for the complete list. Additional status codes can be added by applications by creating an implementation of HttpStatus.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
